Details of expenses (Accounts Payable) from fiscal year 2014 through 2019 including vendor, check, and amounts.

Details of expenses (Accounts Payable) from the beginning of the most recent Fiscal Year, 2020. Includes vendor, checks, and amounts to Jun 30, 2020.
See also dataset Checkbook, which contains historical data starting in Fiscal Year 2014 (July 1, 2013) though Fiscal 2019.
